-- CNPC Discovers Gas in Exploration Well at Turkmenistan's Amu Darya Field
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-09-28T03:54:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-28/cnpc-discovers-gas-in-exploration-well-at-turkmenistan-s-amu-darya-field.html
China National Petroleum Corp.
found gas in an exploration well in the Amu Darya field in
Turkmenistan, the state-owned company said in its online
newsletter today. A gas flow of 1.44 million cubic meters a day
was recorded at the well, according to the newsletter.  To contact the reporter on this story:
